Task 4
1.	Develop a CRUD system with respect to a row of data. 
2.	Expose query built in step number 2 as an API
3.	Expose an API to search by crop or location

Solution:
Steps to deploy in cloud:
1.	Create an EMR cluster in AWS cloud.
2.	Choose a cluster with multiple nodes based on the need to use case.
3.	Submit the spark-submit using EMR gateway (Driver Node).
4.	We are using YARN here as a cluster manager.
5.	We are using multiple worker nodes are tasks execution in parallel. Each task will be run in separate JVM.
6.	Once the transformations are executed using actions, results will be shared to Driver node.
7.	We have Client, cluster and stand alone mode of job execution.
